column5: $20-$30.   I've got two of those things, they definitely don't make them like they used to.

I have a green unit like that one (white gas) due to the technology advances of propane it has little value. I paid 5 dollars for it mainly as an oddity than a useful source of heat in the garage.    Art
$10, they don't put out much heat.  I bought one 10'years ago for $10, I wouldn't pay a penny more.
k thanks guys. It warms up my 4x8 tarp pop up just fine. Just don't open the door too much lol
